{
  "texts": [
    "[16] provide a new SIEM methodology that detects anomalies in a SCADA-controlled water system.",
    "They group the attacks into 14 categories and conduct an evaluation of SIEM performances through operational scenarios.",
    "Cinque et al.",
    "[17] study SIEM in the context of the air traffic control domain which is a mission-critical system.",
    "They discuss the challenges in addressing the massive volumes of highly unstructured text logs that are generated by these systems and their integration with SIEM systems."
  ]
}